			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Father Abdirak is a follower of Loviatar, a goddess that thrives on inflicting pain on others. He is indulging in some private 'worship' (self flagellation). He offers to help alleviate the player's pain by giving them 'penance' - i.e, beating them. &#xA;Loviatar = loh-VEE-a-tar. He is a young and charismatic preacher with a threatening and creepy edge. " />
